<HEADLINE> One of Europe's Biggest Drug Dealers Arrested in Athens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, October 13 (Xinhua) -- Miguel Antonio, one of the
biggest drug dealers in Europe, was arrested in an Athens suburb
Tuesday, Greek police said.
</P>
<P>
Antonio, who was born in Alexandria, Egypt, is a member of the
Latin American cocaine cartel.
</P>
<P>
He was accused of bringing 1,100 kilograms of cocaine from
Colombia to Greece since 1991. 
</P>
