anti-poverty program is currently being implemented, 7,152 people
have been employed over the last few months," he said.
</P>
<P>
"This figure is expected to rise to 14,304 by the end of the
program," Radebe said.
</P>
<P>
The money would be used to improve, among others, roads,
agriculture, school, and other facilities in rural areas, the
minister said.  
