<HEADLINE> Urgent: Taiwan SEF Leader Arrives in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 14 (Xinhua) -- Koo Chen-fu, chairman of the
Taiwan-based Straits Exchange Foundation (SEF), and his party
