<HEADLINE> Vietnam Makes Efforts to Develop Tourism </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, October 14 (Xinhua) -- Vietnam's Tourism Department
mapped out five key tourist sites for development in an efforts
to develop tourism, Vietnam's English newspaper "Vietnam News"
reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
