<HEADLINE> Rusedski Eliminates Kafelnikov in First Round </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, October 13 (Xinhua) -- Briton Greg Rusedski knocked
seventh seed Yevgeny Kafelnikov of Russia out of the CA-Trophy
tennis tournament in the first round here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Rusedski spent nearly two hours in ousting the Russian 6-3,
3-6, 7-6 and set up a second round match with local hero Thomas
Muster.
</P>
