American Todd Martin beat Germany's Nicolas Kiefer 4-6, 6-3,
6-4 and his fellow American Jeff Tarango dismissed Australia's
Jason Stoltenberg 6-2, 6-2 and plays his compatriot world number
one Pete Sampras next. 
